    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Circular ditches that stand alone or form part of a fortification or other earthworks system, often the remains of plowed-out barrows.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
